Interface PibFile

  • All Known Implementing Classes:

      • closeblock

        boolean closeblock​(int zsize)
        Close the current datablock, write the block size to the file and then reposition the file pointer to the end of the block.
        Parameters:
        zsize - The uncompressed block size for compressed blocks, or -1 if the block is not compressed.
        Returns:
        True on success, false on failure.
